  <para style="mt1">KumaHebheru</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Umlobi labalotshelwa incwadi le kabavezwanga kodwa yona ngokwayo iyazivezela injongo yayo. Abayilotshelwayo ngamakholwa esiJuda ayesengozini yokulahlekelwa lukholo lwawo. Indlela umlobi ababingelela ngayo itshengisa ukuthi babese-Ithali. Injongo yogwalo lolu ngeyokutshengisa amandla ezinto eziqinisekileyo ezivezwe nguNkulunkulu ngesivumelwano esitsha kulalawo awesivumelwano esidala esingayisiso saphakade. Abalubalayo bakhuthazwa ukuba bakhangelane lokuhlukuluzwa okuzayo ngokuzinikela kulezo iziqiniseko ezeza ngenxa kaJesu.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ugwalo lolu lulemfundiso, lukhangele imbali ka-Israyeli lemfundiso kumbe indlela yokudumisa ethempelini. Kulemfundiso ezine:</para>
  <para style="ili1">UJesu lensindiso ayilethayo kukhulu kulensindiso eyasakazwa zingilosi (Umlayo kaMosi)</para>
  <para style="ili1">UJesu nguMpostoli wethu (umuntu othunywe nguNkulunkulu ukuzagcwalisisa umsebenzi othile) osingenisa ekuphumuleni okukhulu elizweni lesithembiso ukwedlula lokho uMosi loJoshuwa abangenisa u-Israyeli kukho.</para>
  <para style="ili1">UJesu ngumphristi omkhulu opheleleyo kulabaphristi ababekwa nguMosi</para>
  <para style="ili1">Njengokwenziwa ngabantu bakaNkulunkulu abethembekileyo kusukela endulo, lathi kumele siqhubeke siphila ngethemba kuKhristu wethu sithemba lezozinto ezathenjiswa nguNkulunkulu ezingabonakali ngamehlo. <char style="qt">Samukela umbuso ongeke uzunguzeke</char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="HEB 1"/>
  <para style="s1">ILizwi Lika Nkulunkulu Lokucina: INdodana Yakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 1:1"/>Kudala uNkulunkulu wakhuluma kubokhokho kanenginengi ngabaphrofethi langezindlela ezehlukeneyo <verse eid="HEB 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 1:2"/>kodwa ngalezizinsuku zokucina ukhulume kithi ngeNdodana yakhe, ayibeka ukuba yindlalifa yezinto zonke, yona adala ngayo izulu lomhlaba. <verse eid="HEB 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 1:3"/>INdodana iyikubenyezela kwenkazimulo kaNkulunkulu kanye lomfanekiso wokuba nguye kwakhe uqobo, iqinisa izinto zonke ngelizwi layo elilamandla. Emva kokuba isikufezile ukuhlanjululwa kwezono, yahlala phansi esandleni sokunene sobukhosi ezulwini. <verse eid="HEB 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 1:4"/>Ngakho yaba ngaphezu kwezingilosi ngoba ibizo eyalithola njengelifa lilikhulu kulelazo.<verse eid="HEB 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">INdodana Ingaphezulu Kwezingilosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 1:5"/>Ngoba kukuyiphi ingilosi uNkulunkulu ake wathi kuyo:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:5">“Wena uyiNdodana yami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:5">lamhla sengibe nguYihlo”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 2.7</char></note>?</para>
  <para style="m" vid="HEB 1:5">Kumbe njalo wathi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:5">“Ngizakuba nguYise,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:5">yona izakuba yiNdodana yami”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">2 USamuyeli 7.14; 1 ImiLando 17.13</char></note>?<verse eid="HEB 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 1:6"/>Njalo, lapho uNkulunkulu eletha izibulo lakhe emhlabeni, uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:6">“Zonke izingilosi zikaNkulunkulu kazimkhonze.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 32.43</char></note><verse eid="HEB 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 1:7"/>Lapho ekhuluma ngezingilosi uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:7">“Wenza izingilosi zakhe zibe yimimoya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:7">izinceku zakhe zibe ngamalangabi omlilo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 104.4</char></note><verse eid="HEB 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 1:8"/>Kodwa ngeNdodana uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:8">“Isihlalo sakho sobukhosi, Oh Nkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:8">sizakuma nini lanini,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:8">intonga yokwahlulela okulungileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:8">izakuba yintonga yombuso wakho.<verse eid="HEB 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 1:9"/>Ukuthandile ukulunga wazonda ububi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:9">ngakho uNkulunkulu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:9">uNkulunkulu wakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:9">usekubeke ngaphezu kwabakhula bakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:9">ngokukugcoba ngamafutha entokozo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 45.6-7</char></note><verse eid="HEB 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 1:10"/>Njalo uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:10">“Ekuqaleni, Oh Nkosi, wabeka izisekelo zomhlaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:10">lamazulu angumsebenzi wezandla zakho.<verse eid="HEB 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 1:11"/>Kuzabhubha kodwa wena uzasala;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:11">konke kuzaguga njengesigqoko.<verse eid="HEB 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 1:12"/>Uzakugoqa njengesembatho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:12">kuzantshintshwa njengesigqoko.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:12">Kodwa wena uhlala unjalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:12">leminyaka yakho kayiyikuphela.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 102.25-27</char></note><verse eid="HEB 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 1:13"/>Kukuyiphi ingilosi uNkulunkulu ake wathi kuyo:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:13">“Hlala ngakwesokunene sami;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 1:13">ngize ngenze izitha zakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 1:13">zibe yisinyathelo senyawo zakho”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.1</char></note>?<verse eid="HEB 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 1:14"/>Izingilosi kazisimimoya esebenzayo yini, ethunywe ukukhonza labo abazakudla ilifa lokusindiswa na?<verse eid="HEB 1:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="HEB 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Isixwayiso Sokuba Kunanzelelwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 2:1"/>Ngakho kufanele siqaphelelisise lokho esikuzwileyo ukuze singaduki. <verse eid="HEB 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 2:2"/>Ngoba nxa ilizwi elakhulunywa yizingilosi liqinisa njalo konke ukona lokungalaleli kuthole isijeziso sakho esifaneleyo, <verse eid="HEB 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 2:3"/>pho thina sizaphepha njani nxa singanaki insindiso enkulu kangaka na? Lokhu kusindiswa okwabikwa kuqala yiNkosi, kwafakazwa kithi yilabo abayizwayo. <verse eid="HEB 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 2:4"/>LoNkulunkulu wakufakaza ngezibonakaliso langezimangaliso ezithile, langezipho zikaMoya oNgcwele ezabiwa ngokwentando yakhe.<verse eid="HEB 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Wenziwa Waba Njengabafowabo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 2:5"/>Akusikho ezingilosini abeka khona ngaphansi kwazo ilizwe elizayo esikhuluma ngalo. <verse eid="HEB 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 2:6"/>Kodwa ikhona indawo lapho omunye ofakaza khona esithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 2:6">“Uyini umuntu osungaze uzihluphe ngaye na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 2:6">loba indodana yomuntu ukuba uyinanze na?<verse eid="HEB 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 2:7"/>Wamenza waba mncinyazana kulezingilosi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 2:7">wamethesa umqhele wodumo lobukhosi,<verse eid="HEB 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 2:8"/>wabeka lezinto zonke ngaphansi kwezinyawo zakhe.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 8.4-6</char></note></para>
  <para style="m" vid="HEB 2:8">Ekubekeni izinto zonke ngaphansi kwakhe uNkulunkulu katshiyanga lutho olungekho ngaphansi kwakhe. Kodwa khathesi kasiboni zinto zonke zingaphansi kwakhe. <verse eid="HEB 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 2:9"/>Kodwa sibona yena, owenziwa waba ngaphansanyana kwezingilosi okwesikhatshana, uJesu, ebekwa umqhele wobukhosi lodumo ngoba wavuma ukufa ukuze kuthi ngomusa kaNkulunkulu ezwe ukufa ngenxa yabantu bonke.<verse eid="HEB 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 2:10"/>Ekuletheni amadodana amanengi enkazimulweni, kwakufanele ukuba uNkulunkulu, yena owenza zonke izinto njalo zabakhona ngenxa yakhe, enze umsunguli wokusindiswa kwabo aphelele ngokuhlupheka kwakhe. <verse eid="HEB 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 2:11"/>Ngoba lowo owenza abantu babengcwele kanye lalabo abenziwe baba ngcwele ngabendlunye. Ngakho uJesu kakumyangisi ukuba athi bangabafowabo. <verse eid="HEB 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 2:12"/>Uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 2:12">“Ngizamemezela ibizo lakho kubafowethu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 2:12">ngizahlabelela udumo lwakho phambi kwebandla.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 22.22</char></note><verse eid="HEB 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 2:13"/>Njalo uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 2:13">“Ngizabeka ithemba lami kuye.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 8.17</char></note></para>
  <para style="m" vid="HEB 2:13">Uphinda athi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 2:13">“Mina ngilapha, kanye labantwana uNkulunkulu angiphe bona.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 8.18</char></note><verse eid="HEB 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 2:14"/>Njengoba abantwana belomzimba legazi, laye wahlanganyela ebuntwini babo ukuze kuthi ngokufa kwakhe amchithe lowo ophethe amandla okufa okutsho uSathane, <verse eid="HEB 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 2:15"/>abakhulule ababesebugqilini impilo yabo yonke ngenxa yokwesaba kwabo ukufa. <verse eid="HEB 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 2:16"/>Ngoba impela akusizo ingilosi azisizayo kodwa inzalo ka-Abhrahama. <verse eid="HEB 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 2:17"/>Ngenxa yalokhu kwakumele enziwe afane labafowabo kukho konke ukuze abe ngumphristi omkhulu olesihawu lothembekileyo enkonzweni kaNkulunkulu, lokuba abeyinhlawulo yezono zabantu. <verse eid="HEB 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 2:18"/>Njengoba laye wahlupheka lapho elingwa, uyenelisa ukubasiza abalingwayo.<verse eid="HEB 2:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="HEB 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ungaphezu KukaMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 3:1"/>Ngakho-ke, bafowethu abangcwele, abahlanganyela ekubizweni ezulwini, bekani imicabango yenu kuJesu, umpostoli lomphristi omkhulu esimvumayo. <verse eid="HEB 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 3:2"/>Wathembeka kulowo owambekayo, njengoMosi owayethembekile kuyo yonke indlu kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 3:3"/>UJesu ufunyenwe efanele udumo olukhulu kuloMosi njengomakhi wendlu elodumo olukhulu kulendlu yona ngokwayo. <verse eid="HEB 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 3:4"/>Ngoba yileyo laleyondlu yakhiwa ngumuntu othize kodwa uNkulunkulu ungumakhi wezinto zonke. <verse eid="HEB 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 3:5"/>“UMosi wayethembekile njengenceku kuyo yonke indlu kaNkulunkulu,”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaNani 12.7</char></note> efakaza lokho okwakuzatshiwo ensukwini ezizayo. <verse eid="HEB 3:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 3:6"/>Kodwa uKhristu uthembekile njengendodana endlini kaNkulunkulu. Njalo thina siyindlu yakhe nxa sibambelela ngesibindi langethemba lethu esizincoma ngakho.<verse eid="HEB 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isixwayiso Ngokungakholwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 3:7"/>Ngakho, njengoba uMoya oNgcwele esithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 3:7">“Lamuhla nxa lisizwa ilizwi lakhe,<verse eid="HEB 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 3:8"/>lingazenzi zibe lukhuni inhliziyo zenu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 3:8">njengelakwenza ekuhlamukeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:8">ngesikhathi sokulingwa enkangala,<verse eid="HEB 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 3:9"/>lapho okhokho benu abangihlola khona bangilinga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:9">babona engakwenzayo okweminyaka engamatshumi amane.<verse eid="HEB 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 3:10"/>Yikho-nje ngasithukuthelela isizukulwane leso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:10">njalo ngathi, ‘Inhliziyo zabo zihlezi ziduka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:10">njalo kabazazanga izindlela zami.’<verse eid="HEB 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 3:11"/>Ngakho ngamemezela ngesifungo ekuthukutheleni kwami ngathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:11">‘Kabayikungena ekuphumuleni kwami.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 95.7-11</char></note>”<verse eid="HEB 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 3:12"/>Bonani bazalwane ukuthi kakho omunye wenu olenhliziyo yokona lokungakholwa, ephambukayo kuNkulunkulu ophilayo. <verse eid="HEB 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 3:13"/>Kodwa khuthazanani insuku zonke kusabizwa ngokuthi lamuhla, ukuze angabikhona owenu oba lukhuni ngenxa yokukhohliswa yisono. <verse eid="HEB 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 3:14"/>Ngoba sesingabahlanganyelayo kuKhristu nxa sibambelele ngokuqina kuze kuphele ithemba esasilalo kuqala. <verse eid="HEB 3:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 3:15"/>Njengoba kutshiwo ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 3:15">“Lamuhla nxa lisizwa ilizwi lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:15">lingazenzi zibe lukhuni inhliziyo zenu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 3:15">njengelakwenzayo ekuhlamukeni.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 95.7-8</char></note><verse eid="HEB 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 3:16"/>Babengobani labo abezwayo basebehlamuka na? Akusibo yini bonke labo uMosi abakhupha eGibhithe na? <verse eid="HEB 3:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 3:17"/>Njalo ngobani ayebathukuthelele okweminyaka engamatshumi amane na? Akusibo yini labo abonayo, abazidumbu zabo zawela enkangala na? <verse eid="HEB 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 3:18"/>Ngobani uNkulunkulu abafungela ukuthi kabayikungena ekuphumuleni kwakhe nxa kungayisibo labo abangalalelanga na? <verse eid="HEB 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 3:19"/>Ngakho siyabona ukuthi babengeke bangene ngenxa yokungakholwa kwabo.<verse eid="HEB 3:19"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="HEB 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphumula Kwabantu BakaNkulunkulu NgeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 4:1"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba isithembiso sokungena ekuphumuleni kwakhe silokhu sikhona, kasiqapheleni ukuba kakho phakathi kwenu otholakala engafinyeleli kuso. <verse eid="HEB 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 4:2"/>Ngoba ivangeli latshunyayelwa kithi njengakubo; kodwa ilizwi abalizwayo lalingelasizo kubo ngoba labo abalizwayo kabalihlanganisanga lokholo. <verse eid="HEB 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 4:3"/>Thina esakholwayo siyangena kulokho kuphumula njengoba uNkulunkulu etshilo ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 4:3">“Ngakho ngamemezela ngesifungo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 4:3">ekuthukutheleni kwami ngathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 4:3">‘Kabayikungena ekuphumuleni kwami.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 95.11</char></note>”</para>
  <para style="m" vid="HEB 4:3">Kodwa umsebenzi wakhe wapheleliswa ekudalweni komhlaba. <verse eid="HEB 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 4:4"/>Ngoba kwenye indawo ukhulume ngosuku lwesikhombisa ngala amazwi athi: “Ngakho ngosuku lwesikhombisa uNkulunkulu waphumula kuwo wonke umsebenzi wakhe.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 2.2</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 4:5"/>Njalo endimeni engaphezulu uthi, “Kabayikungena ekuphumuleni kwami.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 95.11</char></note><verse eid="HEB 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 4:6"/>Kulokhu kunjalo ukuthi abanye bazangena kulokho kuphumula, lalabo ivangeli elatshunyayelwa kubo kuqala kabangenanga ngenxa yokungalaleli kwabo. <verse eid="HEB 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 4:7"/>Ngakho uNkulunkulu wabuya wamisa olunye usuku, elubiza ngokuthi Lamuhla, lapho kwathi emva kwesikhathi eside wakhuluma ngoDavida, njengokwakutshiwo mandulo ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 4:7">“Lamuhla nxa lisizwa ilizwi lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 4:7">lingazenzi zibe lukhuni inhliziyo zenu.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 95.7-8</char></note><verse eid="HEB 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 4:8"/>Ngoba aluba uJoshuwa wayebanikile ukuphumula, ngabe uNkulunkulu kakhulumanga muva ngolunye usuku. <verse eid="HEB 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 4:9"/>Ngakho kulokhu kukhona ukuphumula kweSabatha kwabantu bakaNkulunkulu; <verse eid="HEB 4:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 4:10"/>ngoba loba ngubani ongena ekuphumuleni kukaNkulunkulu uyaphumula lakowakhe umsebenzi njengokwenziwa nguNkulunkulu kowakhe. <verse eid="HEB 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 4:11"/>Ngakho-ke, kasenzeni imizamo yonke ukuba singene kulokho ukuphumula, ukuze angabikhona ozawiswa yikulandela isibonelo sakhe sokungalaleli.<verse eid="HEB 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 4:12"/>Ilizwi likaNkulunkulu liyaphila njalo liyasebenza. Libukhali kulenkemba esika inxa zombili, ingena ize yehlukanise umphefumulo lomoya, amalunga lomnkantsho; lahlulela imicabango lomumo wenhliziyo. <verse eid="HEB 4:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 4:13"/>Kukho konke okudaliweyo akulalutho olufihlakeleyo emehlweni kaNkulunkulu. Konke kwambuliwe kwabekwa obala phambi kwamehlo akhe yena okumele sizibike kuye.<verse eid="HEB 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu UmPhristi Omkhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 4:14"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba silomphristi omkhulu kakhulu osengene emazulwini, uJesu iNdodana kaNkulunkulu, kasibambeleleni kakhulu okholweni esiluvumayo. <verse eid="HEB 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 4:15"/>Ngoba kasilamphristi omkhulu onganelisiyo ukusizwela ebuthakathakeni bethu kodwa silaye oseke walingwa ngezindlela zonke njengathi kodwa akazange one. <verse eid="HEB 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 4:16"/>Kasisondeleni esihlalweni sobukhosi somusa ngesibindi ukuze samukele isihawu njalo sithole umusa wokusisiza ezikhathini zokuswela kwethu.<verse eid="HEB 4:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="HEB 5"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 5:1"/>Wonke umphristi omkhulu ukhethwa ebantwini abekwe ukuba abamele ezindabeni ezimayelana loNkulunkulu, ukunikela izipho lemihlatshelo yezono. <verse eid="HEB 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 5:2"/>Ulakho ukubaphatha ngesineke labo abangaziyo abadukayo, njengoba laye uqobo ephethwe yikuba buthakathaka. <verse eid="HEB 5:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 5:3"/>Yikho-nje kumele anikele imihlatshelo yezono zakhe kanye leyezono zabantu. <verse eid="HEB 5:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 5:4"/>Kakho ozethesa udumo lolu phezu kwakhe; kumele abizwe nguNkulunkulu njengo-Aroni.<verse eid="HEB 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 5:5"/>Ngakho loKhristu kazethesanga udumo lokuba ngumphristi omkhulu. Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kuye,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 5:5">“Wena uyiNdodana yami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 5:5">lamuhla sengibe nguYihlo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 2.7</char></note><verse eid="HEB 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 5:6"/>Njalo kwenye indawo uthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 5:6">“Wena ungumphristi kuze kube nini lanini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 5:6">emkhondweni kaMelikhizedekhi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.4</char></note><verse eid="HEB 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 5:7"/>Ngensuku zokuphila kukaJesu emhlabeni, wakhuleka wacela ngokukhala kakhulu langezinyembezi kuye lowo owayengamphephisa ekufeni njalo wezwakala ngenxa yokuzehlisa kwakhe okuhloniphekayo. <verse eid="HEB 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 5:8"/>Lanxa wayeyindodana wafunda ukulalela kulokhu ahlupheka ngakho, <verse eid="HEB 5:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 5:9"/>kwathi lapho esephelelisiwe, waba ngumthombo wokusindiswa okulaphakade wabo bonke abamlalelayo <verse eid="HEB 5:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 5:10"/>wasekhethwa nguNkulunkulu ukuba abe ngumphristi omkhulu, emkhondweni kaMelikhizedekhi.<verse eid="HEB 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isixwayiso Ngokuhlamuka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 5:11"/>Kunengi esingakutsho ngalokho kodwa kunzima ukuchaza ngoba liyaphuza ukufunda. <verse eid="HEB 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 5:12"/>Ngeqiniso, lanxa ngalesisikhathi lifanele ukuba ngabafundisayo, liswela omunye ukuba alifundise amaqiniso okuqala elizwi likaNkulunkulu. Lifuna uchago, hatshi ukudla okuqinileyo! <verse eid="HEB 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 5:13"/>Lowo ophila ngochago, ulokhu elusane, kayazi imfundiso emayelana lokulunga. <verse eid="HEB 5:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 5:14"/>Kodwa ukudla okuqinileyo ngokwabakhulileyo asebazifundisa ukwehlukanisa okuhle kokubi.<verse eid="HEB 5:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="HEB 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 6:1"/>Ngakho kasiyekeleni imfundiso elula ngoKhristu siqhubeke siye ekukhuleni. Kasingasibeki futhi isisekelo sokuphenduka ezenzweni eziholela ekufeni, lezokukholwa kuNkulunkulu, <verse eid="HEB 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 6:2"/>lemfundiso ngemibhaphathizo, lokubekwa kwezandla, lokuvuka kwabafileyo kanye lokwahlulelwa okulaphakade. <verse eid="HEB 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 6:3"/>Njalo nxa uNkulunkulu evuma sizakwenza njalo.<verse eid="HEB 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 6:4"/>Akwenzakali kulabo asebake bakhanyiselwa, asebenambithe isipho sasezulwini, asebehlanganyele kuMoya oNgcwele, <verse eid="HEB 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 6:5"/>asebenambithe ubumnandi belizwi likaNkulunkulu kanye lamandla esikhathi esizayo, <verse eid="HEB 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 6:6"/>njalo nxa behlamuka ukuba babuyiselwe ekuphendukeni ngoba ekulahlekelweni kwabo bayayibethela futhi esiphambanweni iNdodana kaNkulunkulu beyethesa ihlazo phambi kwabantu bonke. <verse eid="HEB 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 6:7"/>Umhlabathi onatha izulu elihlezi lisina phezu kwawo loveza isilimo esilusizo kulabo abawulimayo uthola isibusiso sikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 6:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 6:8"/>Kodwa umhlabathi oveza ameva lokhula kawulasizo njalo usengozini yokuqalekiswa. Ekucineni uzatshiswa.<verse eid="HEB 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 6:9"/>Kodwa lanxa sikhuluma kanje bazalwane abathandekayo, silethemba lezinto ezingcono ngani, izinto ezilokwenza lokusindiswa. <verse eid="HEB 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 6:10"/>UNkulunkulu ulungile, kasoke awukhohlwe umsebenzi wenu lothando elamtshengisa lona njengoba lasiza abantu bakhe njalo liyaqhubeka libasiza. <verse eid="HEB 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 6:11"/>Sifuna omunye lomunye wenu abonakalise ukukhuthala lokhu kuze kube sekupheleni ukuze ithemba lenu liqiniseke. <verse eid="HEB 6:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 6:12"/>Kasifuni ukuba libe ngamavila kodwa ukuba lilingisele labo okwathi ngokukholwa langokubekezela bathola ilifa lalokhu okwakuthenjisiwe.<verse eid="HEB 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubuqotho Besithembiso SikaNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 6:13"/>Lapho uNkulunkulu esenza isithembiso sakhe ku-Abhrahama, njengoba wayengekho omkhulu ayengafunga ngaye, wafunga ngaye yena ngokwakhe <verse eid="HEB 6:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 6:14"/>esithi, “Ngempela ngizakubusisa njalo ngikuphe inzalo enengi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6.14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 22.17</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 6:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 6:15"/>Ngakho emva kokulinda ngokubekezela, u-Abhrahama wathola okwakuthenjisiwe.<verse eid="HEB 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 6:16"/>Abantu bafunga ngomunye omkhulu kulabo njalo isifungo siqinisa lokho okutshiwoyo siqede lokuphikisana konke. <verse eid="HEB 6:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 6:17"/>Njengoba uNkulunkulu wathanda ukuba enze ukungaguquki kwesimo senhloso yakhe kube sobala kuzindlalifa zalokho okwathenjiswayo, wakuqinisa ngesifungo. <verse eid="HEB 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 6:18"/>UNkulunkulu wenza lokhu ukuze kuthi ngezinto ezimbili ezingaguqulekiyo, uNkulunkulu angeke aqambe amanga ngazo, thina esibaleke sabambelela ethembeni esiliphiwayo sikhuthazeke kakhulu. <verse eid="HEB 6:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 6:19"/>Silethemba leli njengensika yemiphefumulo yethu, eliqinileyo njalo eligxilileyo. Lingena endaweni engcwele yangaphakathi ngemva kwamakhetheni <verse eid="HEB 6:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 6:20"/>lapho uJesu owahamba phambi kwethu angena khona ngenxa yethu. Usebe ngumphristi omkhulu emkhondweni kaMelikhizedekhi kuze kube nini lanini.<verse eid="HEB 6:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="HEB 7"/>
  <para style="s1">UMelikhizedekhi Umphristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 7:1"/>UMelikhizedekhi lo wayeyinkosi yaseSalemu lomphristi kaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke. Wahlangabeza u-Abhrahama evela kwehlula amakhosi, wambusisa, <verse eid="HEB 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 7:2"/>u-Abhrahama wamnika okwetshumi kwakho konke. Okwakuqala, ibizo elithi Melikhizedekhi litsho ukuthi “Nkosi yokulunga”; lokuthi futhi, “Nkosi yaseSalemu” kutsho ukuthi “Nkosi yokuthula.” <verse eid="HEB 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 7:3"/>Engelayise loba unina, engelamdabuko, engelakuqala kwensuku loba ukuphela kokuphila njengeNdodana kaNkulunkulu uhlezi engumphristi nini lanini.<verse eid="HEB 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 7:4"/>Ake licabange ukuthi wayemkhulu kangakanani: Lokhokho u-Abhrahama wamnika okwetshumi kwempango! <verse eid="HEB 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 7:5"/>Khathesi umthetho ufuna abenzalo kaLevi ababa ngabaphristi ukuba baqoqe okwetshumi ebantwini, lokhu kutsho abafowabo lanxa abafowabo beyinzalo ka-Abhrahama. <verse eid="HEB 7:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 7:6"/>Umuntu lo kazange alonde umdabuko wakhe usukela kuLevi kodwa waqoqa okwetshumi ku-Abhrahama njalo wambusisa yena lowo owayelezithembiso. <verse eid="HEB 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 7:7"/>Kakulakuthandabuza ukuthi umuntu omncinyane ubusiswa ngomkhulu. <verse eid="HEB 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 7:8"/>Kwesinye isehlakalo, okwetshumi kuthathwa ngabantu abafayo kodwa kwesinye isehlakalo kube ngulowo okuthiwe uyaphila. <verse eid="HEB 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 7:9"/>Umuntu angatsho lokuthi uLevi oqoqa okwetshumi, wanikela okwetshumi ngo-Abhrahama <verse eid="HEB 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 7:10"/>ngoba lapho uMelikhizedekhi ehlangabeza u-Abhrahama uLevi wayelokhu esesemzimbeni kakhokho wakhe.<verse eid="HEB 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu NjengoMelikhizedekhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 7:11"/>Nxa ukuphelela kwakungatholakala ngobuphristi babaLevi njalo ngempela umthetho owaphiwa abantu wasungula lobobuphristi, pho kungani kwakulokhu kudingeka ukuba omunye umphristi abuye evela emkhondweni kaMelikhizedekhi, engasiwemkhondweni ka-Aroni na? <verse eid="HEB 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 7:12"/>Ngoba lapho kulokuguqulwa kobuphristi, kufanele kube lokuguqulwa komthetho futhi. <verse eid="HEB 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 7:13"/>Yena lowo okutshiwo lezizinto ngaye ngowesinye isizwana njalo kakho owalesosizwana owake wakhonza e-alithareni. <verse eid="HEB 7:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 7:14"/>Ngoba kusobala ukuba iNkosi yethu yadabuka koJuda njalo mayelana lalesosizwana uMosi katshongo lutho ngabaphristi. <verse eid="HEB 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 7:15"/>Njalo lokhu esesikutshilo kucace kakhulu nxa omunye umphristi onjengoMelikhizedekhi evela, <verse eid="HEB 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 7:16"/>omunye obe ngumphristi kungayisikho komthetho ngokosendo lwakhe kodwa ngokumayelana lamandla okuphila okungeke kuchithwe. <verse eid="HEB 7:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 7:17"/>Ngoba kumenyezelwe ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 7:17">“Wena ungumphristi kuze kube nini lanini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 7:17">emkhondweni kaMelikhizedekhi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.4</char></note><verse eid="HEB 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 7:18"/>Umthetho wakuqala ubekwe eceleni ngoba wawubuthakathaka njalo ungelasizo <verse eid="HEB 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 7:19"/>(ngoba umthetho kawenzanga lutho olupheleleyo) ngakho kulethwa ithemba elitsha esisondela ngalo kuNkulunkulu.<verse eid="HEB 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 7:20"/>Njalo kwakungayisikho ngaphandle kwesifungo! Abanye babangabaphristi kungekho sifungo, <verse eid="HEB 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 7:21"/>kodwa yena waba ngumphristi ngesifungo lapho uNkulunkulu athi kuye:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 7:21">“INkosi ifungile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 7:21">njalo kayiyikuguqula ingqondo yayo:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 7:21">‘Wena ungumphristi kuze kube nini lanini.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.4</char></note>”<verse eid="HEB 7:21"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 7:22"/>Ngenxa yesifungo lesi, uJesu usebe yisiqiniselo sesivumelwano esingcono.<verse eid="HEB 7:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 7:23"/>Abaphristi labo sebebanengi njengoba babevinjelwa yikufa ukuba baqhubeke besezikhundleni; <verse eid="HEB 7:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 7:24"/>kodwa uJesu uphila kuze kube laphakade, ulobuphristi obuyisimakade. <verse eid="HEB 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 7:25"/>Ngakho ulamandla okubasindisa ngokupheleleyo labo abeza kuNkulunkulu ngaye ngoba uhlezi ephilela ukubancengela.<verse eid="HEB 7:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="HEB 7:26"/>Umphristi omkhulu onjalo wagcwalisa izinswelo zethu, ongongcwele, ongelasici, lohlanzekileyo, lowehlukaniswe lezoni, lophakanyiselwe ngaphezu kwamazulu. <verse eid="HEB 7:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="HEB 7:27"/>Hatshi njengabanye abaphristi abakhulu, yena kadingi kunikela imihlatshelo insuku zonke, kuqala eyezono zakhe, kulandele owezono zabantu. Wabenzela umhlatshelo wezono zabo kwaba kanye kuphela lapho ezinikela. <verse eid="HEB 7:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="HEB 7:28"/>Ngoba umthetho ubeka abantu ababuthakathaka ukuba ngabaphristi abakhulu kodwa isifungo eseza emva komthetho sabeka iNdodana eyenziwe yaba ngepheleleyo kuze kube nininini.<verse eid="HEB 7:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="HEB 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Umphristi Omkhulu Wesivumelwano Esitsha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 8:1"/>Isiqokoqela salokho esikutshoyo yilesi: Silaye umphristi omkhulu onjalo, owahlala phansi esandleni sokunene kwesihlalo sobukhosi soMkhulu ezulwini, <verse eid="HEB 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 8:2"/>okhonzayo endaweni engcwele, ithabanikeli eliqotho elamiswa yiNkosi hatshi ngabantu.<verse eid="HEB 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 8:3"/>Umphristi omkhulu ngamunye ubekelwe ukunikela izipho lemihlatshelo, ngakho kwakufanele ukuba lalo abe lolutho alunikelayo. <verse eid="HEB 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 8:4"/>Aluba wayesemhlabeni wayengayikuba ngumphristi ngoba bevele bekhona abantu abanikela izipho eziphawulwa ngumthetho. <verse eid="HEB 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 8:5"/>Bakhonza endaweni engcwele engumfanekiso lesithunzi salokho okusezulwini. Yikho-nje uMosi waxwayiswa lapho esezakwakha ithabanikeli ngokuthi: “Qaphela ukuba wenze konke njengalokhu owakutshengiswa entabeni.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 25.40</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 8:6"/>Kodwa inkonzo uJesu ayemukeleyo ingcono kuleyabo njengesivumelwano yena angumeli waso singcono kulesidala njalo sakhelwe phezu kwezithembiso ezingcono.<verse eid="HEB 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 8:7"/>Ngoba aluba kwakungelalutho olungalunganga kusivumelwano sakuqala leso, akulasizatho esasingadingelwa esinye. <verse eid="HEB 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 8:8"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathola isici ebantwini wasesithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:8">“Isikhathi siyeza, kutsho iNkosi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:8">lapho engizakwenza khona isivumelwano esitsha</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:8">lendlu ka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:8">kanye lendlu kaJuda.<verse eid="HEB 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 8:9"/>Kasiyikufana lesivumelwano</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:9">engasenza labokhokho babo</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:9">lapho engababamba khona ngesandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:9">ukuba ngibakhuphe eGibhithe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:9">ngoba kabaqhubekanga bethembekile esivumelwaneni sami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:9">ngasengibadela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:9">kutsho iNkosi.<verse eid="HEB 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 8:10"/>Nansi isivumelwano engizasenza lendlu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:10">ngemva kwalesosikhathi, kutsho iNkosi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:10">Ngizabeka imithetho yami ezingqondweni zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:10">ngiyilobe ezinhliziyweni zabo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:10">Ngizakuba nguNkulunkulu wabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:10">bona babengabantu bami.<verse eid="HEB 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 8:11"/>Umuntu kasayikufundisa umakhelwane wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:11">kumbe umfowabo, esithi, ‘Yazi iNkosi,’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 8:11">ngoba bonke bazangazi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:11">kusukela komncinyane wabo kusiya komkhulu.<verse eid="HEB 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 8:12"/>Ngoba ngizabathethelela ububi babo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 8:12">njalo angiyikukhumbula izono zabo futhi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 31.31-34</char></note><verse eid="HEB 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 8:13"/>Ngokuthi isivumelwano lesi “sitsha” wenze esakuqala sangasasebenzi; futhi okungasasebenzi lokugugileyo kuzanyamalala masinyane.<verse eid="HEB 8:13"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="HEB 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Inkonzo Ethabanikeleni Lasemhlabeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 9:1"/>Isivumelwano sakuqala sasilezimiso zokukhonza kanye lendawo engcwele yasemhlabeni. <verse eid="HEB 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 9:2"/>Kwakhiwa ithabanikeli. Ekamelweni lalo lakuqala kwakuloluthi lwesibane, letafula kanye lesinkwa esingcwelisiweyo; lokhu kwakubizwa ngokuthi yiNdawo eNgcwele. <verse eid="HEB 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 9:3"/>Ngemva kwekhetheni lesibili kwakulekamelo elalithiwa yiNdawo eNgcwelengcwele, <verse eid="HEB 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 9:4"/>eyayile-alithare lokutshisela impepha elalihuqwe ngegolide kanye lomtshokotsho wesivumelwano owawuhuqwe ngegolide. Umtshokotsho wakhona wawulembizanyana yemana, lentonga ka-Aroni eyahlumayo kanye lezibhebhedu zamatshe esivumelwano. <verse eid="HEB 9:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 9:5"/>Phezu komtshokotsho kwakulamakherubhi eNkazimulo enze ithunzi phezu kwendawo yomhlatshelo. Kodwa khathesi asingeke silandise okugcweleyo ngalezozinto.<verse eid="HEB 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 9:6"/>Kwathi konke sekulungisiwe kanje, abaphristi bangena njalonjalo ekamelweni langaphandle ukuba benze inkonzo yabo. <verse eid="HEB 9:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 9:7"/>Kodwa umphristi omkhulu nguye kuphela owayengena ekamelweni langaphakathi kanye ngomnyaka, njalo kungeke kwenzeke engelagazi alinikelela yena kanye lezono abantu abazenza bengazi. <verse eid="HEB 9:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 9:8"/>UMoya oNgcwele wayetshengisa ngalokho ukuthi indlela eya eNdaweni eNgcwelengcwele yayingabonakaliswa nxa ithabanikeli lakuqala lilokhu likhona. <verse eid="HEB 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 9:9"/>Lokhu kungumfanekiso walesisikhathi, okubonakalisa ukuthi izipho lemihlatshelo okwakunikelwa kwakunganelisi ukuhlambulula izazela zabakhonzayo. <verse eid="HEB 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 9:10"/>Kuyindaba yokudla lokunatha kuphela kanye lemikhuba eyehlukeneyo yokugeza imilayo yangaphandle komzimba esebenza kuze kufike isikhathi sezimiso ezintsha.<verse eid="HEB 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Igazi LikaKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 9:11"/>Kwathi lapho uKhristu esefikile njengomphristi omkhulu wezinto ezinhle esezikhona, wadabula phakathi kwethabanikeli elikhulu elipheleleyo elingenziwanga ngabantu, okuyikuthi, kalisingxenye yale indalo. <verse eid="HEB 9:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 9:12"/>Kangenanga ngokusebenzisa igazi lembuzi loba elamathole; kodwa wangena kanye kuphela eNdaweni eNgcwelengcwele ngegazi lakhe, esethole ukuhlengwa okulaphakade. <verse eid="HEB 9:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 9:13"/>Igazi lembuzi lelenkunzi lemilotha yamathokazi okufafazwa ebantwini abangahlambulukanga ngokomkhuba kuyabangcwelisa ukuba babe ngabahlambulukileyo ngaphandle. <verse eid="HEB 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 9:14"/>Pho igazi likaKhristu, owazinikela engelasici kuNkulunkulu ngomoya olaphakade, lizazihlambulula kakhulu okungakanani izazela zethu emisebenzini edonsela ekufeni, ukuze sikhonze uNkulunkulu ophilayo!<verse eid="HEB 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 9:15"/>Ngenxa yalokhu uKhristu ungumeli wesivumelwano esitsha ukuze kuthi labo ababiziweyo bathole ilifa elingapheliyo elathenjiswayo njengoba sewafa njengenhlawulo ukuba abakhulule ezonweni abazenzayo esivumelwaneni sakuqala.<verse eid="HEB 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 9:16"/>Mayelana lentando yokwaba ilifa, kuyadingakala ukuba kufakazwe ukufa kwalowo owakwenzayo, <verse eid="HEB 9:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 9:17"/>ngoba intando yokwaba ilifa isebenza kuphela lapho kukhona ofileyo; kayisebenzi nxa lowo owayenzayo elokhu esaphila. <verse eid="HEB 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 9:18"/>Yikho-nje lesivumelwano sakuqala kasifezwanga kungekho gazi. <verse eid="HEB 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 9:19"/>Kwathi uMosi esememezele imilayo yonke yomthetho ebantwini bonke, wathatha igazi lamathole lelempongo ndawonye lamanzi, lewulu ebomvu kanye lezingatsha zehisophi, wachela umqulu kanye labantu bonke. <verse eid="HEB 9:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 9:20"/>Wathi, “Leli ligazi lesivumelwano uNkulunkulu alaye ukuba lisigcine.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9.20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 24.8</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 9:21"/>Ngendlela efanayo wachela ithabanikeli ngegazi kanye lezinto zonke ezisetshenziswayo emikhosini yalo. <verse eid="HEB 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 9:22"/>Ngempela umthetho uphose ufune ukuba izinto zonke zihlanjululwe ngegazi, njalo kungekho kuchithwa kwegazi akukho ukuthethelela.<verse eid="HEB 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 9:23"/>Ngakho kwakufanele ukuba imifanekiso yezinto zasezulwini zihlanjululwe ngemihlatshelo le kodwa izinto zasezulwini uqobo kube ngemihlatshelo engcono kulale. <verse eid="HEB 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 9:24"/>Ngoba uKhristu kangenanga endaweni engcwele eyenziwa ngabantu eyayingumfanekiso waleyo eqotho kuphela; yena wangena ezulwini uqobo, ukuba asimele phambi kukaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 9:25"/>Kangenanga ezulwini ukuba azinikele njalonjalo, njengomphristi omkhulu engena eNdaweni eNgcwelengcwele minyaka yonke legazi elingayisilo lakhe. <verse eid="HEB 9:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="HEB 9:26"/>Ngakho uKhristu wayezahlupheka kanengi kusukela ekudalweni komhlaba. Kodwa khathesi usebonakale kanye kuphela ekupheleni kwezikhathi ukuba asuse isono ngomhlatshelo onguye. <verse eid="HEB 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="HEB 9:27"/>Njengalokhu umuntu wamiselwa ukufa kanye, kuthi emva kwalokho abhekane lokwahlulelwa, <verse eid="HEB 9:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="HEB 9:28"/>ngokunjalo uKhristu wanikelwa kanye ukuba asuse izono zabantu abanengi; njalo uzabonakala okwesibili, hatshi ukuthwala isono, kodwa ukuletha ukusindiswa kulabo abamlindeleyo.<verse eid="HEB 9:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="HEB 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Umhlatshelo KaKhristu Kanye Kuphela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 10:1"/>Umthetho uyisithunzi nje sezinto ezinhle ezizayo kodwa hatshi lokho okuyikho uqobo. Ngenxa yemihlatshelo efanayo ephindwaphindwa kokuphela iminyaka leminyaka ayingeke ibenze baphelele labo abasondela ekukhonzeni. <verse eid="HEB 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 10:2"/>Aluba wawusanelisa, imihlatshelo yayingayikuyekelwa ukunikelwa na? Ngoba abakhonzayo babezahlanjululwa kube kanye kuphela, njalo babengasayikuzizwa belecala lezono zabo. <verse eid="HEB 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 10:3"/>Kodwa imihlatshelo iyisikhumbuzo sezono zeminyaka yonke, <verse eid="HEB 10:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 10:4"/>ngoba akwenzakali ukuba igazi lenkunzi lelembuzi lisuse izono.<verse eid="HEB 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 10:5"/>Ngakho-ke, uKhristu esefikile emhlabeni wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:5">“Umhlatshelo lomnikelo kawukufunanga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:5">kodwa wena wangilungisela umzimba;<verse eid="HEB 10:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 10:6"/>kawuthokozanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:6">ngeminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yesono.<verse eid="HEB 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 10:7"/>Ngasengisithi, ‘Ngilapha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:7">kulotshiwe ngami emqulwini,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:7">ngilande ukuzokwenza intando yakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:7">Oh Nkulunkulu.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 40.6-8</char></note>”<verse eid="HEB 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 10:8"/>Kuqala wathi, “Imihlatshelo leminikelo, iminikelo yokutshiswa kanye leminikelo yesono kawuyifunanga, njalo kayikuthokozisanga” (lanxa umthetho usithi kayenziwe). <verse eid="HEB 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 10:9"/>Wabuya wathi, “Ngilapha, ngilande ukuzokwenza intando yakho.” Ususa okokuqala ukuze amise okwesibili. <verse eid="HEB 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 10:10"/>Njalo ngaleyontando senziwe saba ngcwele ngomhlatshelo womzimba kaJesu Khristu kanye kuphela.<verse eid="HEB 10:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 10:11"/>Insuku zonke umphristi uyema enze imisebenzi yakhe yenkonzo, anikele njalonjalo imihlatshelo minye, engeke isuse izono. <verse eid="HEB 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 10:12"/>Kodwa kwathi umphristi lo esenikelele izikhathi zonke umhlatshelo owodwa wezono, wahlala phansi esandleni sokunene sikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 10:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 10:13"/>Kusukela ngalesosikhathi ulindele izitha zakhe ukuba zibe yisenabelo sakhe, <verse eid="HEB 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 10:14"/>ngoba ngomhlatshelo owodwa usephelelise nini lanini labo abenziwayo ukuba ngcwele.<verse eid="HEB 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 10:15"/>LoMoya oNgcwele uyafakaza kithi ngalokho. Kuqala uthi:<verse eid="HEB 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 10:16"/>“Lesi yisivumelwano engizasenza labo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:16">emva kwalesosikhathi, kutsho iNkosi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:16">Ngizafaka imithetho yami ezinhliziyweni zabo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:16">ngiyilobe lasezingqondweni zabo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 31.33</char></note><verse eid="HEB 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 10:17"/>Wabuya wengeza wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:17">“Izono zabo lezenzo zokungabi lomthetho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:17">angiyikukhumbula futhi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 31.34</char></note><verse eid="HEB 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 10:18"/>Nxa lezi sezithethelelwe, kawusekho umhlatshelo wesono.<verse eid="HEB 10:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inkuthazo Yokubekezela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 10:19"/>Ngakho-ke, bazalwane, njengoba silethemba lokungena eNdaweni eNgcwelengcwele ngegazi likaJesu, <verse eid="HEB 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 10:20"/>ngendlela entsha ephilayo, esiyivulelwe ekhethenini, okuyikuthi umzimba wakhe, <verse eid="HEB 10:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 10:21"/>njalo njengoba silomphristi omkhulu ophethe indlu kaNkulunkulu, <verse eid="HEB 10:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 10:22"/>kasisondeleni kuNkulunkulu ngezinhliziyo eziqotho ngethemba elipheleleyo lokholo; sibe lezinhliziyo ezicheliweyo ukuba sihlanjululwe isazela secala lemizimba yethu igeziswe ngamanzi ahlanzekileyo. <verse eid="HEB 10:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 10:23"/>Kasibambeleleni ngokuqina kulo ithemba esilikholwayo, ngoba lowo owathembisayo uthembekile. <verse eid="HEB 10:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 10:24"/>Njalo kasicabangeni ukuba singakhuthazana njani ethandweni lasezenzweni ezinhle. <verse eid="HEB 10:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 10:25"/>Kasingakudeli ukuhlangana, njengalokhu abanye abajayele ukukwenza kodwa kasikhuthazaneni ikakhulu njengoba sibona uSuku lusondela.<verse eid="HEB 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="HEB 10:26"/>Nxa siqhubeka sisenza izono ngabomu emva kokuba iqiniso sesilazi, kawusekho umhlatshelo wezono, <verse eid="HEB 10:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="HEB 10:27"/>kodwa umlindelo owesabekayo wokwahlulelwa kuphela kanye lomlilo ovuthayo ozaqothula izitha zikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 10:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="HEB 10:28"/>Owawalayo umthetho kaMosi wafa kungela sihawu ngobufakazi babafakazi ababili kumbe abathathu. <verse eid="HEB 10:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="HEB 10:29"/>Pho licabanga ukuthi ufanele ukujeziswa kakhulu kangakanani umuntu owanyathela iNdodana kaNkulunkulu ngaphansi konyawo, ophathe igazi lesivumelwano elamenza waba ngcwele njengento engangcwele, lohlambaza uMoya womusa na? <verse eid="HEB 10:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="HEB 10:30"/>Ngoba thina siyamazi lowo owathi, “Ukuphindisela ngokwami; ngizabuyisela,”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.30 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 32.35</char></note> njalo wathi, “INkosi izakwahlulela abantu bayo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.30 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 32.36; AmaHubo 135.14</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="HEB 10:31"/>Kuyinto eyesabekayo ukuwela ezandleni zikaNkulunkulu ophilayo.<verse eid="HEB 10:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="HEB 10:32"/>Khumbulani insuku zakuqala leziyana emva kokuba selamukele ukukhanya, lapho elaqinisela khona ebunzimeni obukhulu phakathi kokuhlupheka. <verse eid="HEB 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="HEB 10:33"/>Ngezinye izikhathi lenziwa umbukiso wokuhlanjazwa lokuhlukuluzwa; kwathi ngezinye izikhathi lamanyana lalabo ababephathwa kanjalo. <verse eid="HEB 10:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="HEB 10:34"/>Laba lozwelo kulabo ababesentolongweni, lamukela ngentokozo ukuthunjwa kwempahla yenu, ngoba lalikwazi ukuthi lina lilempahla engcono engapheliyo. <verse eid="HEB 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="HEB 10:35"/>Ngakho lingalilahli ithemba lenu; lizavuzwa ngokunengi.<verse eid="HEB 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="HEB 10:36"/>Kuyadingeka ukuba libekezele ukuze kuthi lapho seliyenzile intando kaNkulunkulu, lamukele lokho akuthembisayo. <verse eid="HEB 10:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="HEB 10:37"/>Ngoba,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:37">“Ngesikhatshana nje,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:37">lowo ozayo uzafika</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:37">njalo kasoze aphuze.”<verse eid="HEB 10:37"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="HEB 10:38"/>Kodwa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 10:38">“Olungileyo wami uzaphila ngokukholwa.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:38">Angahlehlela emuva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 10:38">kangiyikuthokoza ngaye.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.38 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHabhakhukhi 2.3-4</char></note><verse eid="HEB 10:38"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="HEB 10:39"/>Kodwa thina kasisibo balabo abahlehlela emuva babhujiswe, kodwa labo abakholwayo basindiswe.<verse eid="HEB 10:39"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="HEB 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Imisebenzi Yokukholwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 11:1"/>Ukukholwa yikuba leqiniso lalokhu esikulindeleyo njalo kuqinisekile ngalokho esingakuboniyo. <verse eid="HEB 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 11:2"/>Lokhu yikho abendulo abanconywa ngakho.<verse eid="HEB 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 11:3"/>Ngokukholwa siyezwisisa ukuthi izulu lomhlaba kwadalwa ngokulaya kukaNkulunkulu, ngoba okubonakalayo kakwenziwanga ngalokho okwakubonakala.<verse eid="HEB 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 11:4"/>Ngokukholwa u-Abheli wanikela kuNkulunkulu umnikelo omuhle kulokaKhayini. Ngokukholwa wanconywa njengomuntu olungileyo, ngesikhathi uNkulunkulu ekhuluma kuhle ngeminikelo yakhe. Njalo ngokukholwa ulokhu ekhuluma, lanxa sewafa.<verse eid="HEB 11:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 11:5"/>Ngokukholwa u-Enoki wasuswa kulumhlaba ephila ukuze angakuzwa ukufa: “Kabonakalanga ngoba uNkulunkulu wayesemthethe.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 5.24</char></note> Engakathathwa, wayenconywe njengowayethokozise uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 11:6"/>Kungelakukholwa akweneliseki ukumthokozisa uNkulunkulu ngoba oza kuye kumele akholwe ukuthi ukhona lokuthi uyabanika umvuzo labo abamdinga ngobuqotho.<verse eid="HEB 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 11:7"/>Ngokukholwa uNowa esexwayisiwe ngezinto ezazingakabonakali, ngokwesaba okungcwele wakha umkhumbi ukuba ahlenge abendlu yakhe. Ngokukholwa kwakhe wawulahla umhlaba waba yindlalifa yokulunga okuza ngokukholwa.<verse eid="HEB 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 11:8"/>Ngokukholwa u-Abhrahama esebizelwe ukuba aye endaweni ayezayamukela muva njengelifa lakhe, walalela wahamba, lanxa wayengakwazi lapho ayesiya khona. <verse eid="HEB 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 11:9"/>Ngokukholwa wahlala elizweni lesithembiso njengesihambi, elizweni elingayisilo lakibo; wahlala emathenteni, njengokwenziwa ngu-Isaka loJakhobe, ababezindlalifa zalelolizwe lesithembiso kanye laye. <verse eid="HEB 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 11:10"/>Ngoba wayelindele idolobho elilezisekelo, elimcandi walo lomakhi walo nguNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 11:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 11:11"/>Ngokukholwa, lanxa u-Abhrahama wayeseluphele loSara eyinyumba, wanikwa amandla okuba lomntwana ngoba wambona njengothembekileyo lowo owayenze isithembiso. <verse eid="HEB 11:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 11:12"/>Ngakho-ke, kusukela kulumuntu oyedwa, owayefana lofileyo, kwavela inzalo enengi njengezinkanyezi emkhathini njalo engeke ibalwe njengenhlabathi ekhunjini lolwandle.<verse eid="HEB 11:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 11:13"/>Abantu bonke laba bafa belokhu bephila ngokukholwa. Kabazamukelanga izinto ezathenjiswayo; bazibona nje kuphela bazithakazelela zikude. Njalo bavuma ukuthi bona babeyizizwe lezihambi emhlabeni. <verse eid="HEB 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 11:14"/>Abantu abakhuluma izinto ezinje babonakalisa ukuthi bafuna ilizwe elingelabo. <verse eid="HEB 11:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 11:15"/>Aluba babecabanga ngelizwe abasuka kulo, babezakuba lethuba lokubuyela. <verse eid="HEB 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 11:16"/>Kodwa-ke bona babefuna ilizwe elingcono, lona elisezulwini. Ngakho uNkulunkulu akumyangisi ukubizwa ngokuthi unguNkulunkulu wabo, ngoba usebalungisele idolobho.<verse eid="HEB 11:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 11:17"/>Ngokukholwa, kwathi u-Abhrahama ehlolwa nguNkulunkulu, wanikela u-Isaka njengomhlatshelo. Yena owayamukele izithembiso wayeseseduze ukuba anikele indodana yakhe eyodwa njalo eyiyo kuphela, <verse eid="HEB 11:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 11:18"/>lanxa uNkulunkulu wayethe kuye, “isizukulwane sakho sizabalwa ngo-Isaka.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 21.12</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 11:19"/>U-Abhrahama wanakana ukuthi uNkulunkulu wayengabavusa abafileyo, njalo nxa kuzekeliswa, wamamukela u-Isaka evela ekufeni.<verse eid="HEB 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 11:20"/>Ngokukholwa u-Isaka wabusisa uJakhobe lo-Esawu ngekusasa labo.<verse eid="HEB 11:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 11:21"/>Ngokukholwa uJakhobe, esesifa wawabusisa wonke amadodana kaJosefa, wasekhonza eyame phezu kwentonga yakhe.<verse eid="HEB 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 11:22"/>Ngokukholwa uJosefa, isiphetho sakhe sesisondele, walandisa ngokuphuma kwabako-Israyeli eGibhithe njalo walayezela ngamathambo akhe.<verse eid="HEB 11:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 11:23"/>Ngokukholwa abazali bakaMosi bamfihla izinyanga ezintathu emva kokuzalwa kwakhe, ngoba babona ukuthi wayengasumntwana nje ojayelekileyo, njalo babengawesabi umthetho wenkosi.<verse eid="HEB 11:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 11:24"/>Ngokukholwa uMosi esekhulile, wala ukuba aziwe njengendodana yendodakazi kaFaro. <verse eid="HEB 11:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 11:25"/>Wakhetha ukuphathwa kubi kanye labantu bakaNkulunkulu kulokuba akholise injabulo yesono okwesikhathi esifitshane. <verse eid="HEB 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="HEB 11:26"/>Wakhetha ihlazo ngenxa kaKhristu njengegugu elikhulu kulenotho yaseGibhithe ngoba wayekhangelele umvuzo phambili. <verse eid="HEB 11:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="HEB 11:27"/>Ngokukholwa wasuka eGibhithe, engalwesabi ulaka lwenkosi; wabekezela ngoba wambona lowo ongabonakaliyo. <verse eid="HEB 11:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="HEB 11:28"/>Ngokukholwa wagcina iPhasika lokuchelwa kwegazi, ukuze umbulali wamazibulo angawathinti amazibulo ako-Israyeli.<verse eid="HEB 11:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="HEB 11:29"/>Ngokukholwa abantu badabula phakathi koLwandle oluBomvu njengasemhlabathini owomileyo, kodwa kwathi amaGibhithe ezama ukwenzanjalo agalula.<verse eid="HEB 11:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="HEB 11:30"/>Ngokukholwa imiduli yaseJerikho yadilika emva kokuba abantu beyibhode okwensuku eziyisikhombisa.<verse eid="HEB 11:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="HEB 11:31"/>Ngokukholwa uRahabi isifebe, ngoba wamukela inhloli, kabulawanga kanye lalabo ababengalaleli.<verse eid="HEB 11:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="HEB 11:32"/>Kuyini okunye engingakutsho? Kangilasikhathi sokulandisa ngoGidiyoni, loBharakhi, loSamsoni, loJeftha, loDavida, loSamuyeli kanye labaphrofethi, <verse eid="HEB 11:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="HEB 11:33"/>abanqoba imibuso ngokukholwa benza okulungileyo njalo bathola okwakuthenjisiwe; bona abavala imilomo yezilwane, <verse eid="HEB 11:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="HEB 11:34"/>bacitsha ukuvutha kwamalangabi, baphepha lasebukhalini benkemba; ubuthakathaka babo baphenduka baba ngamandla; njalo baba lamandla empini bawachitha amabutho ezizweni. <verse eid="HEB 11:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="HEB 11:35"/>Abesifazane bamukela abafayo babo sebevuselwe ekuphileni futhi. Abanye bahlukuluzwa njalo bala ukukhululwa, ukuze bathole ukuvuka ekufeni okuhle. <verse eid="HEB 11:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="HEB 11:36"/>Abanye bahozwa batshaywa, kwathi abanye babotshwa ngamaketane bafakwa entolongweni. <verse eid="HEB 11:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="HEB 11:37"/>Batshaywa ngamatshe, baqunywa ngesaha baba yiziqa ezimbili; babulawa ngenkemba. Bahamba begqoke izikhumba zezimvu lezikhumba zembuzi, beswela, behlukuluzwa, bephathwa kubi, <verse eid="HEB 11:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="HEB 11:38"/>umhlaba kubo wawungabafanele. Bantula enkangala lasezintabeni lasezimbalwini kanye lasemilindini emhlabathini.<verse eid="HEB 11:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="HEB 11:39"/>Bonke laba banconywa ngokukholwa kwabo, kodwa kakho phakathi kwabo owathola okwakuthenjisiwe. <verse eid="HEB 11:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="HEB 11:40"/>Thina uNkulunkulu wayesimisele okuhle ukuze kuthi sebe kanye lathi bapheleliswe.<verse eid="HEB 11:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="HEB 12"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 12:1"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba sihanqwe lixuku elikhulu kangaka labafakazi, kasikulahleni konke okusivimbelayo kanye lesono esisibopha lula njalo kasigijimeni ngokubekezela kulo umjaho ophawulelwe thina. <verse eid="HEB 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 12:2"/>Kasikhangeleni kuJesu, uMqalisi loMphelelisi wokukholwa kwethu, okwathi ngentokozo eyayibekwe phambi kwakhe wabekezelela isiphambano, engananzi ihlazo laso, wahlala phansi esandleni sokunene sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="HEB 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 12:3"/>Cabangani ngaye owabekezelela ukuphikiswa okungaka ngabantu abayizoni ukuze lingabi buthakathaka lilahle ithemba.<verse eid="HEB 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UNkulunkulu Ulaya Abantwana Bakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 12:4"/>Ekulweni kwenu lesono, kalimelananga laso kwaze kwaba sebangeni lokuchitha igazi lenu. <verse eid="HEB 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 12:5"/>Njalo selilikhohliwe lelizwi lokulikhuthaza elikhuluma kini njengamadodana elithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 12:5">“Ndodana yami, ungeyisi ukulaya kweNkosi.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 12:5">Njalo ungalahli ithemba lapho ikukhuza,<verse eid="HEB 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 12:6"/>ngoba uThixo ulaya labo abathandayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 12:6">abuye ajezise bonke abamukela njengendodana.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Izaga 3.11-12</char></note><verse eid="HEB 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 12:7"/>Bekezelelani ukuhlupheka njengokulaywa; uNkulunkulu uliphatha njengabantwana bakhe. Kambe yibaphi abantwana abangalaywa nguyise na? <verse eid="HEB 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 12:8"/>Nxa lingalaywa (umuntu wonke uyalaywa), liyabe lingabantwana abazalwa ngokungekho emthethweni njalo abangasiwo amadodana lamadodakazi uqobo. <verse eid="HEB 12:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 12:9"/>Phezu kwalokho, sonke sake saba labobaba abasilayayo njalo sabahlonipha ngenxa yalokho. Pho kufanele sizehlise kakhulu okungakanani kuBaba wemimoya yethu njalo siphile! <verse eid="HEB 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 12:10"/>Obaba basilaya okwesikhatshana ngababekubona kukuhle, kodwa uNkulunkulu usilaya ukuba sisizakale, ukuba sihlanganyele ebungcweleni bakhe. <verse eid="HEB 12:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 12:11"/>Akukho kulaywa okukhanya kukuhle ngalesosikhathi, kodwa kubuhlungu. Kodwa muva, kuletha isivuno sokulunga lokuthula kulabo abafundiswa yikho.<verse eid="HEB 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 12:12"/>Ngakho-ke, qinisani izingalo zenu ezibuthakathaka lamadolo enu axegayo. <verse eid="HEB 12:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 12:13"/>“Lungiselani inyawo zenu izindlela ezibekekileyo,”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Izaga 4.26</char></note> ukuze abaqhulayo bangagogeki, kodwa basiliswe.<verse eid="HEB 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isixwayiso Ngokwala UNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 12:14"/>Zamani kakhulu ukuhlalisana ngokuthula labantu bonke lokuba ngcwele; kungekho bungcwele kakho ozayibona iNkosi. <verse eid="HEB 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 12:15"/>Bonani ukuthi kakho oswela umusa kaNkulunkulu kanye lokuthi akulampande ebabayo ekhulayo ukuba idale uhlupho ingcolise abanengi. <verse eid="HEB 12:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 12:16"/>Bonani ukuthi kakho oyisifebe, loba ongakhonzi uNkulunkulu njengo-Esawu okwathi ngenxa yokudla kunye wathengisa amalungelo elifa lakhe okuba lizibulo. <verse eid="HEB 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 12:17"/>Muva, njengoba lisazi, lapho esefuna ukuzuza isibusiso lesi waliwa. Wayengeke enze kube lokuguquka kwengqondo, lanxa wafuna isibusiso leso ngezinyembezi.<verse eid="HEB 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Intaba Yokwesaba Lentokozo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 12:18"/>Kalizanga entabeni engathintwayo njalo ebhebha umlilo; ebumnyameni lasekufiphaleni lesiphepho; <verse eid="HEB 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 12:19"/>ekukhaleni kwecilongo loba ilizwi elinjalo elikhulumayo, okwenza labo abalizwayo bacela ukuba kungabi lelizwi elikhulunywa kubo futhi, <verse eid="HEB 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 12:20"/>ngoba babengeke bakumele ukulaywa okwakusithi: “Lenyamazana ingathinta intaba, kumele itshaywe ngamatshe.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 19.12-13</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 12:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 12:21"/>Okwabonwayo kwakusesabeka kakhulu uMosi waze wathi, “Ngiyathuthumela ngenxa yokwesaba.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 9.19</char></note><verse eid="HEB 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 12:22"/>Kodwa lina lize eNtabeni iZiyoni, iJerusalema lasezulwini, umuzi kaNkulunkulu ophilayo. Lize kuzinkulungwane lezinkulungwane zezingilosi ezihlangane ngentokozo <verse eid="HEB 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 12:23"/>ebandleni lezibulo, ezimabizo azo alotshiwe ezulwini. Lize kuNkulunkulu, umahluleli wabantu bonke, emimoyeni yabantu abalungileyo abaphelelisiweyo, <verse eid="HEB 12:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 12:24"/>kuJesu umeli wesivumelwano esitsha, lasegazini elicheliweyo elikhuluma ilizwi elihle kulegazi lika-Abheli.<verse eid="HEB 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 12:25"/>Bonani ukuthi kalimenqabeli lowo okhulumayo. Nxa bengaphephanga lapho benqabela lowo owabaxwayisa emhlabeni, koba kuncane kangakanani kithi, nxa sidela lowo osixwayisa ezulwini na? <verse eid="HEB 12:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="HEB 12:26"/>Ngalesosikhathi ilizwi lakhe lanyikinya umhlaba, kodwa khathesi usethembisile wathi: “Ngizaphinda njalo futhi nginyikinye, hatshi umhlaba kuphela, kodwa lamazulu futhi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHagayi 2.6</char></note> <verse eid="HEB 12:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="HEB 12:27"/>Amazwi la “njalo futhi” atsho ukususwa kwalokho okunganyikinyiswa, okuyikuthi izinto ezadalwayo, ukuze kuthi lokho okungeke kunyikinyiswe kusale.<verse eid="HEB 12:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="HEB 12:28"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba sisamukela umbuso ongeke unyikinywe, kasibongeni njalo sikhonze uNkulunkulu ngokufaneleyo ngenhlonipho langokwesaba, <verse eid="HEB 12:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="HEB 12:29"/>ngoba “uNkulunkulu wethu ungumlilo oqothulayo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.29 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 4.24</char></note><verse eid="HEB 12:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="HEB 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Izixwayiso Zokucina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="HEB 13:1"/>Qhubekani lithandana njengabazalwane. <verse eid="HEB 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="HEB 13:2"/>Lingakhohlwa ukwamukela izihambi ngoba ngokwenza njalo abanye abantu bamukela izingilosi bengazi. <verse eid="HEB 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="HEB 13:3"/>Khumbulani abasentolongweni ngokungathi lani liyizibotshwa kanye labo, kanye lalabo abaphethwe kubi ngokungathi lani uqobo liyahlupheka.<verse eid="HEB 13:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="HEB 13:4"/>Ukuthathana kumele kuhlonitshwe ngumuntu wonke, kuthi lomendlalo wokuthathana uhlale uhlambulukile ngoba uNkulunkulu uzakwahlulela isifebe labo bonke abahlobongayo. <verse eid="HEB 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="HEB 13:5"/>Ekuphileni kwenu xwayani ukuthanda imali lisuthiseke ngalokho elilakho, ngoba uNkulunkulu wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 13:5">“Kangisoze ngilitshiye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 13:5">kangisoze ngilidele.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 31.6</char></note><verse eid="HEB 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="HEB 13:6"/>Ngakho siyatsho ngethemba sithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="HEB 13:6">“INkosi ingumsizi wami; kangiyikwesaba.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="HEB 13:6">Umuntu angenzani kimi na?”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.6-7</char></note><verse eid="HEB 13:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="HEB 13:7"/>Khumbulani abakhokheli benu, abakhuluma ilizwi likaNkulunkulu kini. Cabangani okwavela endleleni yokuphila kwabo lilingisele ukukholwa kwabo. <verse eid="HEB 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="HEB 13:8"/>UJesu Khristu uyafana izolo lanamhla kanye laphakade.<verse eid="HEB 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="HEB 13:9"/>Lingathatheki ngazozonke inhlobo zemfundiso engaziwayo. Kuhle ukuba inhliziyo zethu ziqiniswe ngumusa, hatshi yikudla komkhuba okungelasizo kulabo abakudlayo. <verse eid="HEB 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HEB 13:10"/>Thina sile-alithare lapho labo abakhonza ethabanikeleni bengelalungelo lokudlela kulo.<verse eid="HEB 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="HEB 13:11"/>Umphristi omkhulu uletha igazi lezifuyo eNdaweni eNgcwelengcwele njengomnikelo wesono kodwa izidumbu zazo ziyatshiswa ngaphandle kwezihonqo. <verse eid="HEB 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="HEB 13:12"/>Ngokunjalo uJesu laye wahlupheka ngaphandle kwesango ledolobho ukuba enze abantu bakhe babengcwele ngegazi lakhe. <verse eid="HEB 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="HEB 13:13"/>Ngakho-ke, kasiyeni kuye ngaphandle kwezihonqo silehlazo alithwalayo. <verse eid="HEB 13:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="HEB 13:14"/>Ngoba lapha kasiladolobho elimiyo njalo, kodwa sidinga idolobho elizayo.<verse eid="HEB 13:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="HEB 13:15"/>Ngakho, ngoJesu kasinikeleni njalonjalo kuNkulunkulu umhlatshelo wokubonga, isithelo sezindebe ezivuma ibizo lakhe. <verse eid="HEB 13:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="HEB 13:16"/>Njalo lingakhohlwa ukwenza okulungileyo kanye lokwabela abanye ngoba uNkulunkulu uyathokoza ngemihlatshelo enje.<verse eid="HEB 13:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="HEB 13:17"/>Lalelani abakhokheli benu njalo lithobele amandla abo. Bayalilinda njengabantu okumele balandise ngani. Balaleleni ukuze umsebenzi wabo uthokozise njalo ungasindi ngoba lokho akungeke kube lusizo kini.<verse eid="HEB 13:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="HEB 13:18"/>Sikhulekeleni. Sileqiniso ukuthi silesazela esihle njalo sifisa ukuhlala ngobuqotho ngezindlela zonke. <verse eid="HEB 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="HEB 13:19"/>Ikakhulu ngiyalincenga ukuba likhuleke ukuze ngibuyiselwe kini masinyane.<verse eid="HEB 13:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izibusiso Lokuvalelisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="HEB 13:20"/>Sengathi uNkulunkulu wokuthula, owavusa iNkosi yethu uJesu kwabafileyo ngegazi lesivumelwano esingapheliyo, lowoMalusi omkhulu wezimvu, <verse eid="HEB 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="HEB 13:21"/>angalihlomisa ngakho konke okulungele ukwenza intando yakhe, njalo sengathi angasebenza phakathi kwethu lokho okumthokozisayo ngoJesu Khristu, udumo kalube kuye kuze kube nini lanini. Ameni.<verse eid="HEB 13:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="HEB 13:22"/>Bazalwane, ngiyalincenga ukuba libekezelele ilizwi lami lokuqonqosela kwami ngoba ngililobele incwadi emfitshane nje.<verse eid="HEB 13:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="HEB 13:23"/>Ngithanda ukuba likwazi ukuthi umzalwane wethu uThimothi usekhululwe. Angafika masinyane ngizakuza laye sizelibona.<verse eid="HEB 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="HEB 13:24"/>Bingelelani bonke abakhokheli benu kanye labantu bakaNkulunkulu bonke.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="HEB 13:24">Abavela e-Ithali bayalibingelela.<verse eid="HEB 13:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="HEB 13:25"/>Umusa kawube lani lonke.<verse eid="HEB 13:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="HEB 13"/>
</usx>
